  <ShootingAccuracyPawn.label>武器掌握</ShootingAccuracyPawn.label>
  <!-- EN: How well a shooter can hold a gun steady when aiming and compensate for recoil.\n\nThe total sway is calculated as:\n(4.5 - weapon handling) * weapon sway factor\n\nThe recoil per shot is determined by multiplying this value against the weapon's inherent recoil amount and increases after every shot in a burst. -->
  <ShootingAccuracyPawn.description>衡量一个射手在进行射击时压枪来维持稳定射击的能力。\n\n 总的射击误差计算公式为：\n （4.5-武器掌握）*武器面板误差系数\n\n 每次射击的产生的后坐力由该数值乘以武器固有的后坐力确定，并且在武器连发的过程中每次射击后该数值都会逐渐增加</ShootingAccuracyPawn.description>
  
